  "body": "<p>In case you missed my announcement, I'll be LIVE on HSN at 10am and 3pm EST today (March 24)! Hope you'll tune in and check out the awesome bundles that are available. In celebration, we are highlighting some more projects using the Plus One products.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fab94a640167dfa6.jpg?v=1782535738\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Office Organizer Board by <a href=\"http://www.kleinworthco.com/2014/03/office-organizer-board.html/2\">Kleinworth &amp; Co.</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b9dbc2497a646b1f.jpg?v=1782535741\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Embroidered Spring Banner by <a href=\"http://lizoncall.com/2014/03/19/embroidered-spring-banner/\">Liz on Call</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/849d2ca9bada38d3.jpg?v=1782535745\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>DIY Gift Wrap by <a href=\"http://www.thescrapshoppeblog.com/2014/03/diy-gift-wrap-using-scrapbook-paper.html\">The Scrap Shoppe</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/750590af6b7f2e13.jpg?v=1782535747\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Embroidered Banner by <a href=\"http://www.ajennuinelife.com/2014/03/embroidered-banner-with-amy-tangerine.html\">A Jennuine Life</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a246eefe5f17ef98.jpg?v=1782535750\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Spring Party Decoration by <a href=\"http://waffleflower.com/2014/03/spring-partyhome-decoration-tulip-or-pinwheel/\">Waffle Flower</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/597e46f3cd4ea143.jpg?v=1782535752\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Instagram Photo Display by <a href=\"http://